{"tid":2294752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS走下台「一一向媒體鞠躬」　記者感動發文：他們沒有忘記初心","createTime":"2020-11-21T09:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T12:07:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"541b89c64fc2e3b9b7cca310ff80ee5db3248d10","tid":2294752,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"南韓天團防彈少年團（BTS）以新專輯《BE》回歸，這張專輯從詞曲創作、內容企劃發想、影像製作等，全都出自團員之手，成為「最忠實呈現BTS」的一張專輯。在記者會上，他們對於採訪媒體們的態度，也獲得記者讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5284/d5284558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5284%2Fd5284558.jpg&h=4e569edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團為新專輯《BE》舉辦記者會，久違與媒體見面。（圖／翻攝自BTS推特）<br />\n<br />\n成員SUGA日前因舊傷動手術，目前正在復原靜養中，因此缺席了記者會。不過團員們在拍照時，還是為他留了位置。而隊中大哥JIN今年滿28歲，到了南韓入伍的年限，他於記者會中也再次強調：「只要國家需要我，就會隨時入伍，其實成員間也經常討論兵役問題，我們都打算如期服役。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5284/d5284559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5284%2Fd5284559.jpg&h=82fc9e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團在記者會台上，特地留了SUGA的位置（原為左二）。（圖／翻攝自BTS推特）<br />\n<br />\n由於因為疫情關係，上回他們舉辦記者會時，是採取線上的方式。當時成員V還表示：「本來以為會見到各位記者，所以穿了漂亮的衣服來，可是⋯⋯（台下都沒有人）。」20日記者會上，與久違的媒體們見面，柾國和JIMIN、J-Hope都表達了緊張又興奮的心情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5284/d5284560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5284%2Fd5284560.jpg&h=a43eb9ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團以新專輯《BE》回歸。（圖／翻攝自BTS推特）<br />\n<br />\n韓媒也放出現場影片，在記者會結束後，成員們下台卻沒有直接離場，而是一一向現場媒體鞠躬致意後才離開。一名在場記者也拍下了這一幕並表示：「過去記者會結束後，歌手們會到台下留下祝福的話，不過這傳統已經消失得差不多了。他們成為世界明星後，也沒有忘記初心，讓人感到溫暖。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5284/d5284557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5284%2Fd5284557.jpg&h=97768c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓記者發文稱讚防彈少年團。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n該名記者也特別提到，隊長RM總是以「夥伴」、「為BTS添上翅膀的人」稱呼媒體們，雖然乍看像是拍馬屁，但現場完全不會有這種感覺，「因為能感受到是真心說出這些話，語言比想像的力量更強大。」"},{"pid":"0024641dd3ce11944a6ca86f2702f0c768a570e5","tid":2294752,"uid":256796,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"G chi😳✊🏻💘"},{"pid":"1e9efd3f2f312d9f4617c310e17bfbdf6de6111b","tid":2294752,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"抵佢地紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6603ed0346a9d72521e7e06192fa3707d9714611","tid":2294752,"uid":228223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"有品典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7284868bcf87e41f5754c5aeddb157c153d1834","tid":2294752,"uid":290895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e880b5af62a1fe01e9ff3cfac711da33aa19fa9e","tid":2294752,"uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"最緊要唔好向支那鞠躬"},{"pid":"e7819ef87f5dc4a99320257f8768f7f8dc12f9ba","tid":2294752,"uid":157255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"最愛BTS 世界第一<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}